room_title: Escape room "Apartment 205" by Enigma Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_address: 7805 West Sunset Blvd #200, Los Angeles, CA 90046
room_description: Today your special investigations unit is assigned a bomb threat case. A bio-chemical weapon purchase leads you to an ordinary apartment in the middle of Hollywood. It belongs to a middle aged jeweler, and his track record is spotless. But there can be no mistakes. Find the bomb and deactivate it in time!
